when-we-were-young-festival-3519567">观看艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne) 在 When Were Young 音乐节上以 All Time Low 演唱《Sk8er Boi》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
律师称 Kanye West 将不会竞选 2024 年总统https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-will-not-run-for-president-in-2024-lawyer-says-3519541?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kanye-west-will-律师称不会​​竞选 2024 年总统Hollie GeraghtyMon, 23 Oct 2023 06:48:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3519541 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肯伊·韦斯特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位说唱歌手将在明年的选举前结束他的竞选活动</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-will-not-run-for-president-in-2024-lawyer-says-3519541">律师称 Kanye West 将不会竞选 2024 年总统的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肯伊·韦斯特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-not-running-for-president-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·韦斯特 (Kanye West)</a>的律师发表声明称，他将不会竞选 2024 年总统。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/inside-the-west-wing-what-sort-of-president-would-kanye-west-be-2702132">西翼内部：坎耶·韦斯特会成为什么样的总统？</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位现在名叫叶的说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-confirms-running-president-2024-2574336">早在 2019 年就首次宣布打算竞选公职</a>。他后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-concedes-2020-presidential-election-2808637">承认参加 2020 年总统选举</a>，但表示将参加 2024 年总统选举。</p><p>他的私人律师布鲁斯·马克斯现已在<em><a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/politics/politics-features/kanye-presidential-run-2024-ending-1234858651/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">滚石杂志</a></em>的一份声明中证实：“他不是 2024 年的公职候选人。”</p><p>据报道，他的律师正在努力结束这位艺术家的竞选活动。不参选的决定也反映在 Kanye 2020（West 的政治委员会） <a href="https://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/605/202310159598051605/202310159598051605.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">10 月份向联邦选举委员会</a>提交的文件中，该文件显示，今年 1 月至 9 月，所有 50 个州都没有分配给主要开支的资金。</p><p>其最近的报告期似乎筹集了零美元，而委员会手头现金不到 25,000 美元（20,580 英镑）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3519553" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3519553" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3519553" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-california-2023.jpg" alt="肯伊·韦斯特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-california-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-california-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-california-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-california-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-california-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/kanye-west-california-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3519553" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 6 月 16 日，坎耶·维斯特 (Kanye West) 离开加利福尼亚州比佛利山庄的 e.baldi 餐厅（图片来源：MEGA/GC Images）</figcaption></figure><p>去年，韦斯特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-enlists-alt-right-voice-milo-yiannopoulos-for-2024-presidential-campaign-3352990">招募了另类右翼声音米洛·扬诺普洛斯 (Milo Yiannopoulos)</a>协助他 2024 年的竞选活动。由于有报道称他被解雇，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/has-milo-yiannopoulos-already-been-fired-from-kanye-west-presidential-campaign-3360744">于 12 月退出竞选活动</a>，随后于 5 月再次受聘。</p><p>韦斯特的竞选总统计划因一年的争议而蒙上阴影，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-backlash-3325627">他去年因一系列有争议的反犹太言论而受到谴责</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adidas-ends-kanye-west-deal-in-light-of-rappers-anti-semitic-comments-3335494">这也导致他与运动服装品牌阿迪达斯分道扬镳。</a></p><p>去年，阿迪达斯因称他的煽动性言论“不可接受、充满仇恨且危险”而断绝了合作关系。韦斯特当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-doesnt-believe-in-the-term-anti-semitism-its-not-factual-3330802">否认这些言论是种族主义言论</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-antisemitic-comments-dropped-lawyer-talent-agency-3334864">据报道，其他几家公司和组织也已与韦斯特断绝了联系</a>，其中包括他的律师和预订机构。</p><p>据报道，本月早些时候，韦斯特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-reportedly-files-yews-trademark-application-after-antisemitism-controversy-3511010">提交了几项使用“Yews”的商标申请</a>。</p><p>商标律师乔什·格本 (Josh Gerben) 声称，韦斯特已通过他的公司 Ox Paha Inc. 提交了 26 项商标申请。他们报告称，这些商标包括教育、音乐流媒体、电视、游戏、服装等领域的申请。所有被指控的文件的清单可以<a href="https://www.gerbenlaw.com/blog/kanye-west-files-26-trademark-applications-to-protect-yews/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到。</p><p>据报道，这位说唱歌手还在创作新音乐，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-reportedly-debuts-new-album-at-private-listening-party-in-italy-3508319">在意大利的私人聆听派对上首次推出了新专辑</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-will-not-run-for-president-in-2024-lawyer-says-3519541">律师称 Kanye West 将不会竞选 2024 年总统的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
